methods.comment: Returns the LayoutModel index of the item that was just returned via #next().

methods.javadoc:
Returns the LayoutModel index of the next item that will be returned via {@link #next()}.
@return index of the next Layout item returned, or null if no additional items are present
methods.name: getNextIndex
methods.comment: Returns the LayoutModel index of the next item that will be returned via #next().

return.comment: index of the next Layout item returned, or null if no additional items are present

methods.name: getPreviousIndex
methods.comment: Returns the LayoutModel index of the previous item that was returned via #next().

return.comment:
index of the previous Layout item returned, or null if this iterator hasn't been
 used yet.
